pageType: content
background:
  type: solid
  color: "$white"
notes: "Comandos de validação por superfície. make só cobre as suítes Python compartilhadas; cada app JS valida a si mesmo."
elements:
  - elementId: kicker
    elementType: text
    bounds: [56, 34, 500, 16]
    content:
      style: "$kicker"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: 22 · VALIDAÇÃO
  - elementId: title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [56, 56, 848, 36]
    content:
      style: "$title"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: Como verificar cada camada você mesmo
  - elementId: title-rule
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [56, 102, 56, 3]
    shapeName: rect
    fill: {type: solid, color: "$accent"}
  - elementId: code-panel
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [56, 124, 560, 352]
    shapeName: rect
    fill: {type: solid, color: "$ink"}
  - elementId: code
    elementType: text
    bounds: [74, 140, 524, 324]
    content:
      fontSize: 9.5
      color: "#D8DDE3"
      lineHeight: 1.6
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p><span style="color:#8B9199;"># Substrato Python compartilhado (raiz)</span></p>
        <p><span style="color:#F2B794;">$</span> make install && make test && make test-core && make test-substrate</p>
        <p><span style="color:#F2B794;">$</span> python3 -m learner.substrate            <span style="color:#8B9199;"># regenera views</span></p>
        <p><span style="color:#F2B794;">$</span> python3 -m learner.substrate --check    <span style="color:#8B9199;"># drift, sem escrever</span></p>
        <p><span style="color:#F2B794;">$</span> python3 -m learner.gate --dry-run       <span style="color:#8B9199;"># gate verificador</span></p>
        <p style="margin-top:8px"><span style="color:#8B9199;"># Runner de checklist</span></p>
        <p><span style="color:#F2B794;">$</span> python3 -m engines.openclaw --preview</p>
        <p><span style="color:#F2B794;">$</span> python3 -m pytest engines/openclaw/tests/</p>
        <p style="margin-top:8px"><span style="color:#8B9199;"># Apps JS (cada um se valida)</span></p>
        <p><span style="color:#F2B794;">$</span> cd engines/codexDojo && pnpm run lint && pnpm run test && pnpm run build</p>
        <p><span style="color:#F2B794;">$</span> cd engines/codexdojo-os-prototype && npm run lint && npm run test \</p>
        <p>    && npm run build && npm run test:smoke</p>
        <p><span style="color:#F2B794;">$</span> cd engines/pixelDojo && pnpm run lint && pnpm run test \</p>
        <p>    && pnpm run typecheck && pnpm run build && pnpm run smoke</p>
        <p><span style="color:#F2B794;">$</span> cd engines/voxelDojo && <span style="color:#8B9199;"># mesma sequência (pnpm, recursiva)</span></p>
        <p style="margin-top:8px"><span style="color:#8B9199;"># Trilha verificada do projeto 02 (Node)</span></p>
        <p><span style="color:#F2B794;">$</span> cd curriculum/02_key_value_store/node-impl \</p>
        <p>    && npm run lint && npm run test:coverage && npm run build</p>
  - elementId: n-head
    elementType: text
    bounds: [652, 124, 252, 16]
    content: {fontSize: 10, color: "$ink", bold: true, letterSpacing: 1.2, align: [left, middle], wrap: false, text: "OBSERVAÇÕES"}
  - elementId: n-rule
    elementType: line
    bounds: [652, 144, 252, 2]
    viewBox: [252, 2]
    points: "0,1 252,1"
    border: {style: solid, width: 1, color: "$line"}
  - elementId: n-body
    elementType: text
    bounds: [652, 156, 252, 320]
    content:
      style: "$body"
      fontSize: 10
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p>· <strong>Nunca rode npm/pnpm install na raiz</strong> — a raiz é um umbrella, não um app;</p>
        <p style="margin-top:8px">· os targets <strong>make</strong> cobrem apenas as suítes Python compartilhadas (minimaxDojo, openclaw, learner/substrate, gate) — não são um build geral do repo;</p>
        <p style="margin-top:8px">· <strong>smoke</strong> = Playwright jogando de verdade (2D/3D) ou subindo os 4 webServers do OS em 3 viewports;</p>
        <p style="margin-top:8px">· evidência gerada (<span style="color:$accentDark;">evidence.ndjson</span>, live-evidence*) é <strong>trilha de auditoria</strong>: fica versionada; screenshots de smoke são artefatos, não source;</p>
        <p style="margin-top:8px">· o gate pode ser ensaiado com <strong>--dry-run</strong>: decide sem escrever nada.</p>
  - elementId: footer-line
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [56, 508, 848, 1]
    shapeName: rect
    fill: {type: solid, color: "$line"}
  - elementId: footer-left
    elementType: text
    bounds: [56, 516, 400, 14]
    content: {style: "$tiny", align: [left, middle], wrap: false, text: "AI DEVSCHOOL — COMO FUNCIONA"}
  - elementId: footer-page
    elementType: text
    bounds: [820, 516, 84, 14]
    content: {style: "$tiny", align: [right, middle], wrap: false, text: "23"}
